description.excerpt: Reproduction of MobileNet V3 architecture as described in Searching for MobileNetV3 by Andrew Howard, Mark Sandler, Grace Chu, Liang-Chieh Chen, Bo Chen, Mingxing Tan, Weijun Wang, Yukun Zhu, Ruoming Pang, Vijay Vasudevan, Quoc V. Le, Hartwig Adam on ILSVRC2012 benchmark with PyTorch framework.
74.3% MobileNetV3-Large and 67.2% MobileNetV3-Small model on ImageNet

installation.excerpt: To do this, you can use the following script: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/soumith/imagenetloader.torch/master/valprep.sh

invocation.excerpt: Download the ImageNet dataset and move validation images to labeled subfolders.
